---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Us - AI Marketing Experts | Skyabove"
  description="Meet the Skyabove team: AI experts across the United States and Sri Lanka with 25 years of marketing experience and 5+ years of deep AI expertise. Masters of AI-powered marketing automation."
>
  <Navigation />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <span class="hero-label">About Skyabove</span>
        <h1 class="hero-title">Masters of AI-Powered Marketing</h1>
        <p class="hero-description">
          A global team of AI experts combining 25 years of marketing mastery with cutting-edge artificial intelligence to transform how businesses grow.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team Overview -->
  <section class="team-overview">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="overview-grid">
        <div class="overview-card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
              <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Global Team</h3>
          <p>AI experts across the United States and Sri Lanka working as one unified team</p>
        </div>

        <div class="overview-card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
              <path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>25 Years Experience</h3>
          <p>Deep expertise in marketing strategy, business automation, and growth optimization</p>
        </div>

        <div class="overview-card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
              <path d="M12 16v-4"></path>
              <path d="M12 8h.01"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>5+ Years AI Mastery</h3>
          <p>Leading the AI revolution since before ChatGPT went mainstream</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story -->
  <section class="our-story">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="story-content">
        <div class="story-header">
          <span class="section-label">Our Story</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Built for the AI Age</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="story-text">
          <p>
            Long before AI became a buzzword, we were deep in the trenches—experimenting with machine learning models,
            testing early AI platforms, and discovering how artificial intelligence could revolutionize marketing and business automation.
          </p>

          <p>
            With <strong>25 years of marketing and business automation experience</strong>, we've seen every trend, tested every platform,
            and learned what actually drives results. But it wasn't until AI emerged that we found the tool that could finally deliver
            on marketing's biggest promise: personalization, automation, and optimization at true scale.
          </p>

          <p>
            For over <strong>5 years, we've been masters of AI</strong>—not just users, but experts who understand these systems at a fundamental level.
            We don't wait for blog posts to tell us about new AI capabilities. We're testing them the day they launch. We're pushing the limits.
            We're discovering what's possible before anyone else even knows to look.
          </p>

          <p>
            Today, Skyabove is a <strong>global team spanning the United States and Sri Lanka</strong>, united by a singular mission:
            harness AI to deliver marketing results that were impossible just a few years ago.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AI Expertise -->
  <section class="ai-expertise">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="expertise-header">
        <span class="section-label">AI Mastery</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Always on the Cutting Edge</h2>
        <p class="section-description">
          We don't just use AI tools—we master them. Every new platform, every new capability, every breakthrough.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="expertise-grid">
        <div class="expertise-category">
          <h3>Generative AI Platforms</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>ChatGPT (OpenAI)</strong> - GPT-4, GPT-4 Turbo, advanced prompt engineering</li>
            <li><strong>Claude (Anthropic)</strong> - Claude 3.5 Sonnet, extended context capabilities</li>
            <li><strong>Gemini (Google)</strong> - Multimodal AI, enterprise integrations</li>
            <li><strong>Perplexity AI</strong> - Real-time research and market intelligence</li>
            <li><strong>Llama (Meta)</strong> - Open-source models for custom solutions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="expertise-category">
          <h3>AI Content Creation</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Midjourney</strong> - Custom visual content and brand imagery</li>
            <li><strong>DALL-E 3</strong> - Product visualization and ad creative</li>
            <li><strong>Runway ML</strong> - AI video editing and generation</li>
            <li><strong>ElevenLabs</strong> - AI voice generation for video and audio</li>
            <li><strong>Jasper & Copy.ai</strong> - Marketing copy at scale</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="expertise-category">
          <h3>AI Marketing Tools</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Smartly.io</strong> - Automated ad buying and optimization</li>
            <li><strong>Pattern89</strong> - Creative performance prediction</li>
            <li><strong>Seventh Sense</strong> - AI-powered email timing</li>
            <li><strong>Mutiny</strong> - Website personalization at scale</li>
            <li><strong>Drift</strong> - Conversational AI and chatbots</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="expertise-category">
          <h3>AI Analytics & Insights</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Tableau AI</strong> - Natural language analytics</li>
            <li><strong>Looker</strong> - AI-driven business intelligence</li>
            <li><strong>Pecan AI</strong> - Predictive analytics and forecasting</li>
            <li><strong>Improvado</strong> - AI marketing intelligence</li>
            <li><strong>ThoughtSpot</strong> - Search-powered insights</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="expertise-category">
          <h3>AI Development</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>OpenAI API</strong> - Custom GPT integrations</li>
            <li><strong>Anthropic API</strong> - Claude for enterprise solutions</li>
            <li><strong>LangChain</strong> - AI application frameworks</li>
            <li><strong>Pinecone</strong> - Vector databases for AI memory</li>
            <li><strong>Make.com & Zapier</strong> - No-code AI automation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="expertise-category">
          <h3>Emerging AI Platforms</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>AI Search (SGE, Perplexity)</strong> - Optimization for AI discovery</li>
            <li><strong>Agentic AI Systems</strong> - Autonomous task completion</li>
            <li><strong>Multimodal AI</strong> - Text, image, video, audio integration</li>
            <li><strong>Custom LLMs</strong> - Fine-tuned models for specific use cases</li>
            <li><strong>AI Agents</strong> - Autonomous marketing assistants</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="expertise-cta">
        <p class="expertise-tagline">
          <strong>We're not just keeping up with AI—we're staying ahead of it.</strong><br>
          The day a new AI capability launches, we're already testing how it can improve your marketing.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Sets Us Apart -->
  <section class="differentiators">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="diff-header">
        <span class="section-label">What Sets Us Apart</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Human Expertise + AI Power</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="diff-grid">
        <div class="diff-card">
          <div class="diff-number">01</div>
          <h3>Deep AI Understanding</h3>
          <p>
            We don't just use AI tools—we understand how they work. This means we can push them further,
            combine them in novel ways, and extract value others miss.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="diff-card">
          <div class="diff-number">02</div>
          <h3>25 Years of Marketing Wisdom</h3>
          <p>
            AI accelerates everything, but strategy still matters. Our decades of marketing experience ensure
            AI amplifies proven strategies, not just automates bad ideas.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="diff-card">
          <div class="diff-number">03</div>
          <h3>Always Learning, Always Adapting</h3>
          <p>
            The AI landscape changes weekly. We're constantly testing new platforms, discovering new capabilities,
            and implementing innovations before your competitors even hear about them.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="diff-card">
          <div class="diff-number">04</div>
          <h3>Global Team, Local Focus</h3>
          <p>
            Our US and Sri Lanka teams work in tandem, providing 24/7 coverage, diverse perspectives,
            and cost-effective expertise without sacrificing quality.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="diff-card">
          <div class="diff-number">05</div>
          <h3>Results-Driven AI Implementation</h3>
          <p>
            We measure everything. AI isn't magic—it's measurable advantage. Our clients see 3.8x ROAS,
            259% revenue growth, and 127% more leads because we optimize for outcomes, not just outputs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="diff-card">
          <div class="diff-number">06</div>
          <h3>Human-Centric AI</h3>
          <p>
            AI works best when guided by human creativity and strategic thinking. We use AI to amplify
            human expertise, not replace it—delivering personalized, authentic marketing at scale.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Results -->
  <section class="results-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="results-header">
        <span class="section-label">Proven Track Record</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">AI-Powered Results</h2>
        <p class="section-description">
          Our expertise translates directly to measurable business outcomes
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="results-grid">
        <div class="result-stat">
          <div class="stat-number">3.8x</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Average ROAS</div>
          <p class="stat-description">Across all marketing campaigns using our AI systems</p>
        </div>

        <div class="result-stat">
          <div class="stat-number">259%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Revenue Growth</div>
          <p class="stat-description">Average year-over-year growth for clients</p>
        </div>

        <div class="result-stat">
          <div class="stat-number">320+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">AI Implementations</div>
          <p class="stat-description">Custom AI solutions deployed for businesses</p>
        </div>

        <div class="result-stat">
          <div class="stat-number">10x</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Faster Content</div>
          <p class="stat-description">Production speed with AI-powered workflows</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Approach -->
  <section class="approach">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="approach-header">
        <span class="section-label">How We Work</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Our AI-First Approach</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="approach-steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Understand Your Business</h3>
            <p>
              We start by deeply understanding your market, customers, and growth goals. AI is powerful,
              but only when applied strategically to real business challenges.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Design AI-Powered Systems</h3>
            <p>
              We architect complete AI marketing systems—not just individual tools. Everything from
              content creation to analytics to optimization works together intelligently.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Implement & Train</h3>
            <p>
              We deploy cutting-edge AI tools and train your team on how to work alongside them.
              You'll understand not just what the AI does, but why it works.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">4</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Optimize Continuously</h3>
            <p>
              AI learns and improves over time—and so do we. We continuously test new approaches,
              implement new AI capabilities, and optimize for better results every month.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="about-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Work with AI Experts Who Get Results</h2>
        <p>
          25 years of marketing experience. 5+ years of AI mastery. A global team ready to transform your business.
        </p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Get Started Today</a>
          <a href="tel:+19517600896" class="btn btn-secondary btn-large">Call (951) 760-0896</a>
        </div>
        <p class="cta-pricing">Comprehensive AI marketing services starting at $3,500/month</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    background: var(--bg-darker);
    padding: 8rem 0 5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 1200px;
    height: 1200px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--primary) 0%, transparent 70%);
    opacity: 0.05;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--primary-light);
    background: var(--bg-card);
    padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--text-primary) 0%, var(--primary-light) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .hero-description {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .team-overview {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }

  .overview-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .overview-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .overview-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .card-icon {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-light));
    border-radius: 16px;
    color: white;
  }

  .overview-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .overview-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .our-story {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--bg-darker);
  }

  .story-content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .story-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--primary-light);
    background: var(--bg-card);
    padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .story-text p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .story-text strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .ai-expertise {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }

  .expertise-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-description {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 1rem auto 0;
  }

  .expertise-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .expertise-category {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .expertise-category h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--primary-light);
  }

  .expertise-category ul {
    list-style: none;
  }

  .expertise-category li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .expertise-category li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .expertise-category strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .expertise-cta {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-darker);
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 2px solid var(--primary);
  }

  .expertise-tagline {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .expertise-tagline strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  .differentiators {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--bg-darker);
  }

  .diff-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .diff-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  .diff-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .diff-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .diff-number {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: var(--gradient-1);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .diff-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .diff-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .results-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }

  .results-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .results-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .result-stat {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: var(--gradient-1);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .stat-description {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .approach {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--bg-darker);
  }

  .approach-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .approach-steps {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .step:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  }

  .step-number {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-light));
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
  }

  .step-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .step-content p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-cta {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }

  .cta-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta-content > p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: #ff6b35;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #ff8542;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.4);
